help_info = "This program will generate a randomly generated strong password for you or you can create your own password. You will store these passwords in the background and be able to look up what your password is whenever you need it. This program developed by Deniz Varıcı\n\n help -> list of commands\n info -> also list of commands\n list -> show all your passwords\n add -> add new data to your password list\n delete -> delete a data by platform name\n destroy -> delete all password data\n update -> update current platforms password\n get -> get a spesific platform's password\n hidden-list -> get platform's list without passwords\n clear -> clear console history\n exit -> shutdowns the program\n quit -> also shutdowns the program\n"
